###admin login
POST http://localhost:5000/common-api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email":"admin@gmail.com",
    "password":"admin"
}

###read all users and authors(email)

GET http://localhost:5000/admin-api/emails

###block or activate user or author

PUT http://localhost:5000/admin-api/userStatus
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email":"user1@gmail.com",
    "isUserActive":true
}